8, 175.7427, 175.9538, 175.5137, 176.1234, 176.6916, 177.7902, 177.8437, 178.56, 178.2, 178.0289, 176.1101, 176.3289, 176.6897, 176.9096, 177.8756, 176.2546, 178.8348, 180.6576, 180.9391, 182.0159, 182.4025, 181.856, 181.8917, 181.6972, 182.813, 182.6313, 181.9496, 182.7948, 181.5278, 183.2077, 183.8911, 184.704, 185.1508, 184.9404, 185.3143, 186.7763, 186.4216, 186.0852, 183.8602, 183.1442, 183.4188, 183.1281, 183.1493, 182.1232, 182.5575, 181.5737, 180.4209, 178.803, 178.2633, 178.8321, 176.9828, 176.0751, 175.6032, 175.4147, 173.1326, 174.288, 175.0901, 174.746, 175.4256, 174.8742, 174.9455, 174.4776, 172.5868, 172.1475, 174.5172, 174.2542, 172.037, 173.2332, 172.9264, 171.2831, 174.2124, 172.5288, 171.2311, 170.968, 174.2123, 172.107, 171.9049, 170.3452, 171.1711, 170.8932, 174.694, 177.0375, 176.5519, 175.9808, 179.9514, 179.6109, 179.1979, 179.0469, 176.422, 177.5148, 177.5873, 174.2767, 174.5397, 175.4436, 175.0083, 172.0933, 173.3513, 171.7168, 172.6294, 170.6419, 167.6722, 168.7083, 167.6728, 165.2553, 167.2147, 168.3044, 168.093, 166.8468, 170.3906, 170.1645, 169.8375, 169.5779, 168.687, 167.5508, 167.3779, 166.4699, 165.2999, 165.9735, 163.858, 162.6991, 160.2723, 163.3422, 161.207, 161.8731, 160.9847, 161.8377, 162.6548, 163.2634, 165.2424, 164.8915, 163.9185, 163.6144, 163.1243, 162.7628, 162.2182, 161.6292, 162.017, 162.6788, 164.2632, 166.3069], "summary_html": "<h1>量价齐飞 FLY 因子 | 通过 (Sharpe 1.21)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>该因子捕捉\"量价齐飞\"现象——当价格与成交量（换手率）呈现高度正相关时，暗示短期过度投机行为，预示未来价格回落。核心逻辑基于行为金融学：散户处置效应和庄家投机周期导致\"放量上涨\"的股票在下一期表现不佳。因子值越高（量价同向越强），做空信号越强。</p>\n<p>将此逻辑迁移到商品期货市场：用收盘价与换手率（volume/opi）的滚动相关系数作为因子，截面排名后反向做多空组合。高 FLY 品种（过度投机）做空，低 FLY 品种做多。</p>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>核心因子（原文定义）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">FLY_t^i = \\text{corr}(P_\\tau^i, \\text{Turn}_\\tau^i), \\quad \\tau \\in [t-W+1, t]</div>\n<p>其中：</p>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">P_\\tau^i</span>：品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 在时刻 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\tau</span> 的收盘价</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{Turn}_\\tau^i = \\text{Volume}_\\tau^i / \\text{OPI}_\\tau^i</span>：换手率代理变量（成交量 / 持仓量）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">W</span>：回望窗口（最优 60 日）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>仓位构建：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_t^i = (0.5 - \\text{rank}_t^{cs}(FLY_t^i)) \\times 2</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_t^i = \\text{vol\\_target\\_scale}(\\text{rebalance\\_hold}(\\text{signal}, H), \\sigma_{target}=0.15)</div>\n<p>变形因子：</p>\n<ul><li>FLY_R2: <span class=\"math-tex\">FLY_{R2} = \\rho^2</span>（忽略方向，只看拟合度）</li>\n<li>FLY_cut: 截尾处理，去除低价 40% 数据后再算相关性</li>\n<li>FLY_vol: 直接用 volume 替代 turnover</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数列表</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>默认值</th><th>范围</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td>corr_window</td><td>60</td><td>[20, 60]</td><td>滚动相关系数窗口</td></tr><tr><td>hold_days</td><td>40</td><td>[20, 60]</td><td>再平衡持仓周期</td></tr><tr><td>vol_target</td><td>0.15</td><td>[0.10, 0.20]</td><td>年化波动率目标</td></tr><tr><td>factor_direction</td><td>negative</td><td>固定</td><td>高 FLY 做空</td></tr><tr><td>turnover_proxy</td><td>volume/opi</td><td>固定</td><td>换手率代理变量</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (扣费后 4bps)</td><td><strong><strong>1.21</strong></strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>198.4%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>163.3%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-66.4%</td></tr><tr><td>最终 NAV</td><td>18.97</td></tr><tr><td>截面 IC</td><td>0.0152</td></tr><tr><td>时序 IC</td><td>0.0074 (ICIR 0.23)</td></tr><tr><td>因子库相关性</td><td>0.355 (new_signal)</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>Top 3 变体</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>变体</th><th>Sharpe</th><th>年化收益</th><th>MaxDD</th></tr><tr><td>fly_turn_60_h40_vt20_cs</td><td>1.21</td><td>198%</td><td>-66%</td></tr><tr><td>fly_turn_60_h40_cs</td><td>1.21</td><td>197%</td><td>-68%</td></tr><tr><td>fly_turn_60_h40_vt10_cs</td><td>1.21</td><td>197%</td><td>-69%</td></tr><tr><td>fly_vol_60_h40_cs</td><td>1.20</td><td>181%</td><td>-34%</td></tr><tr><td>fly_turn_40_h40_cs</td><td>1.12</td><td>178%</td><td>-75%</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th></tr><tr><td>0.22</td><td>0.17</td><td>0.23</td><td>0.28</td><td>0.27</td><td>0.36</td><td>0.24</td><td>-0.01</td><td>0.30</td><td>0.25</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.54, turnover 0.91, vol_target_scale 在 rebalance 之前导致换手过高</td><td>修复操作顺序: rebalance_hold 先于 vol_target_scale; 扩展 hold 到 [20,40]; 添加 turnover/volume 两种 proxy</td><td>Sharpe 0.54 -&gt; 1.21, 多个变体 &gt;0.8</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>所有 gate 通过, Sharpe 1.21; window=60 + hold=40 + cs 归一化最优; R2 (corr^2) 表现差; IC gate 变体被去重</td><td>聚焦 window [40,60], 加 hold=60; 添加 vol_target [0.10, 0.20] 变体; 移除表现差的 R2 和短窗口</td><td>Sharpe 微升至 1.2146; hold=60 反而变差 (0.51); vol_target 变化影响不大</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>收敛: Sharpe 1.21 稳定, 年度 Sharpe 均&gt;0 (除 2023 -0.01); 半程 Sharpe: 前半 1.11, 后半 1.51</td><td>确认最优参数; decision=skip</td><td>最终 Sharpe 1.21, 策略稳定</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R1 -&gt; R2 的 Sharpe 翻倍（0.54 -&gt; 1.21）源于两个改动：(1) 修正 rebalance/vol_target 顺序避免每日换仓，(2) 将 hold_days 从 20 增至 40 大幅降低换手成本。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货（59 个品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 约 40 个交易日（月度偏长）</li>\n<li><strong>因子类型</strong>: 截面反转/过度投机类</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 原文为 A 股选股因子，跨资产到商品期货有效但 IC 偏低（0.015 截面, 0.007 时序）\n<p>- 2023 年 Sharpe 接近零，该年策略几乎无收益 - 截面标准化（_cs）对提升 Sharpe 作用很大，说明因子量纲在品种间差异较大 - 换手率代理变量（volume/opi）非精确换手率，在 opi 数据缺失品种退化为纯 volume</p>"}